snippet.title: Caddicarus
snippet.description:
I'm Caddy, and I do long stupid videos. Some on movies, some on Nursery Rhyme VHS tapes, some on Peppa Pig, and mostly about video games. From PS1 classics to brand new modern Steam trash, I go through it all and go slightly insane. Enjoy.
